      "message": "If you chdir, binary_dir is no longer valid if relative.\n\nNone of the tests should be sensitive to cwd. I’m able to run this script without cwd\u003dcrashpad_dir on Mac, which makes me question this change. Is a Windows-specific test like end_to_end_test.py or crashpad_handler_test? We should probably fix that then.",
